## [V6.0.0] — 2026-03-20 — The Three-Layer Architecture Release

### Added
- Three-Layer Architecture: Heartbeat / Behavior / Brain.
- Axiom 0 (Soul Supremacy), 0.1 (Quality > Speed), 0.2 (Intent Interpretation), 0.3 (Override Gate).
- Deployment Tier Detector. The Brain pipeline. Hallucination Recovery Protocol.
- Cost Transparency. Dynamic Agent Spawning. Advanced Search with Validation.
- Token Economy Protocol. Strict Task Separation (Axiom 7). Progress Bar system.
- 5-Layer Prompt Architecture + CTRL_PROMPT + TASKFORCE + DEBUG restored.
- Voice Mode with spoken evidence tags. ZMA 6 vulnerability vectors.
- Meta-Update full safety pipeline. Behavior modules (Micro/Standard/Extended).

